{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"3634","heading":"Assumed Federal income tax on competitive products income","label":"3634 Assumed Federal income tax on competitive products income","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/ptIV/ch36/schII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe Internal Revenue Code of 1986, referred to in subsec. (a), is classified to Title 26, Internal Revenue Code."],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Definitions","label":"a .—Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the term “assumed Federal income tax on competitive products income” means the net income tax that would be imposed by chapter 1 of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 on the Postal Service’s assumed taxable income from competitive products for the year; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the only activities of such corporation were the activities of the Postal Service allocable under section 2011(h) to competitive products; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the only assets held by such corporation were the assets of the Postal Service allocable under section 2011(h) to such activities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Computation and Transfer Requirements","label":"b .—Computation and Transfer Requirements","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"compute its assumed Federal income tax on competitive products income for such year; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"transfer from the Competitive Products Fund to the Postal Service Fund the amount of that assumed tax.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":".—Deadline for Transfers","label":"c .—Deadline for Transfers","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s3634","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs3634%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Any transfer required to be made under this section for a year shall be due on or before the January 15th next occurring after the close of such year.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}
